#: ../../admin-manual/installation/upgrading.rst:16
msgid ""
"While we have tried to make this document usable by readers with a broad "
"range of technical knowledge, it may be too complex if you have no previous "
"experience with installing web applications or using the Linux command line."
msgstr ""
"私たちは、さまざまな技術知識を持つ読者が利用できるようにこのドキュメントを作成しましたが、もしあなたがウェブアプリケーションのインストールやLinuxコマンドラインの使用経験がない場合には、内容が難しすぎる可能性があります。"

#: ../../admin-manual/installation/upgrading.rst:20
msgid ""
"Additionally, consider disabling your web site during the upgrade. Redirect "
"your users to a \"Down for maintenance\" page temporary using your web "
"server redirection capabilities, or you can put your site in read-only mode "
"while performing the upgrade."
